<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Conecta Seguros — Nicolás Álvarez · Productor Asesor</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --azul:    #0B1D3A;
  --azul-m:  #1A3A6B;
  --azul-l:  #2563EB;
  --gold:    #B8923A;
  --gold-l:  #D4AF6A;
  --gold-p:  #F0D89A;
  --blanco:  #FAFAF8;
  --crema:   #F5F0E8;
  --texto:   #1A1A2E;
  --muted:   #6B7280;
  --borde:   rgba(184,146,58,0.2);
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  background: var(--blanco);
  color: var(--texto);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(11,29,58,0.97);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borde);
  padding: 16px 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
.nav-logo {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.nav-logo-main {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
}
.nav-logo-sub {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-top: 1px;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center;
}
.nav-link {
  font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  transition: color .2s;
}
.nav-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.nav-cta {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 2px;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--azul); }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--azul);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  padding: 120px 0 80px;
}

/* Fondo con textura sutil */
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(184,146,58,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(37,99,235,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
}

/* Líneas elegantes */
.hero-lines {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-lines::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; right: 280px; bottom: 0;
  width: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(184,146,58,0.2) 30%, rgba(184,146,58,0.2) 70%, transparent);
}
.hero-lines::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; right: 260px; bottom: 0;
  width: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(184,146,58,0.08) 30%, rgba(184,146,58,0.08) 70%, transparent);
}

.hero-wrap {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
  gap: 80px; align-items: center;
}

.hero-content {}

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 24px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  animation: fadeUp .6s both;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before {
  content: ''; width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 76px);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--blanco);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  animation: fadeUp .6s .1s both;
}
.hero-title em {
  font-style: italic; color: var(--gold);
  display: block;
}

.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 19px);
  font-weight: 300; color: rgba(250,250,248,0.6);
  line-height: 1.75; max-width: 520px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  animation: fadeUp .6s .2s both;
}
.hero-sub strong { color: var(--blanco); font-weight: 500; }

.hero-btns {
  display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeUp .6s .3s both;
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--gold); color: var(--azul);
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 2px;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-l); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(184,146,58,.25); }
.btn-secondary {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 2px;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }

/* CARD NICO */
.hero-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid var(--borde);
  border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
  animation: fadeUp .6s .2s both;
  position: relative;
}
.hero-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-p), var(--gold));
}
.hero-card-inner { padding: 36px 32px; }
.hero-card-foto {
  width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid var(--borde);
  background: var(--azul-m);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 32px;
}
.hero-card-nombre {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 24px; color: var(--blanco);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.hero-card-cargo {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero-card-mat {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.hero-card-aseg {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.aseg-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
}
.aseg-item::before {
  content: ''; width: 4px; height: 4px;
  border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0;
}
.hero-card-wa {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  background: #25D366; color: #fff;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 3px;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
}
.hero-card-wa:hover { background: #22c55e; }

/* SERVICIOS */
.servicios {
  padding: 100px 0;
  background: var(--crema);
  position: relative;
}
.servicios::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--azul), var(--gold), var(--azul));
}

.wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px; }

.sec-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
}
.sec-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 30px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }

.sec-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--texto); margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.sec-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

.sec-sub {
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 64px;
}

.servicios-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
}

.servicio-card {
  background: var(--blanco);
  padding: 40px 32px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  transition: all .3s;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
}
.servicio-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.servicio-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(184,146,58,0.08);
  position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 20px; line-height: 1;
}
.servicio-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.servicio-titulo {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--texto); margin-bottom: 10px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.servicio-desc {
  font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.65; position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

/* POR QUÉ */
.porque { padding: 100px 0; background: var(--azul); }

.porque-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px; align-items: center;
  margin-top: 64px;
}

.porque-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }
.porque-item { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; }
.porque-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; width: 56px;
}
.porque-item-content {}
.porque-item-title {
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--blanco);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.porque-item-desc { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.65; }

.porque-visual {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid var(--borde);
  border-radius: 4px; padding: 48px 40px;
  position: relative;
}
.porque-visual::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-p));
}
.porque-cita {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--blanco); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.porque-cita::before { content: '\201C'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 48px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.4em; margin-right: 4px; }
.porque-firma { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
.porque-firma-nombre {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px; color: var(--blanco);
}
.porque-firma-cargo {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
}
.porque-firma-mat {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* FORMULARIO */
.cotizacion { padding: 100px 0; background: var(--crema); }

.cot-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px; align-items: start;
  margin-top: 64px;
}

.cot-info {}
.cot-info-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--texto); margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2;
}
.cot-info-desc {
  font-size: 17px; color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px;
}
.cot-contactos { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
.cot-contacto {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  font-size: 16px; color: var(--texto);
  text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s;
}
.cot-contacto:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.cot-contacto-icon {
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--azul); color: var(--gold);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;
}

.cot-form {
  background: var(--azul);
  border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(11,29,58,0.15);
}
.cot-form-top { background: var(--gold); height: 4px; }
.cot-form-inner { padding: 44px 40px; }
.cot-form-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 28px; color: var(--blanco);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
.form-label {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 6px; display: block;
}
.form-input, .form-select {
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 3px; padding: 13px 16px;
  color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  outline: none; transition: border-color .2s;
}
.form-input:focus, .form-select:focus { border-color: var(--gold); }
.form-input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
.form-select option { background: #0B1D3A; }

.btn-cotizar {
  width: 100%; background: var(--gold); color: var(--azul);
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 16px; border-radius: 3px; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s; margin-top: 8px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
}
.btn-cotizar:hover { background: var(--gold-l); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.cot-nota {
  text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-top: 14px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  background: var(--azul);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--borde);
  padding: 56px 0;
}
.footer-inner {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px;
}
.footer-logo-wrap {}
.footer-logo-main {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.footer-logo-sub {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); text-transform: uppercase;
}
.footer-info {
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  line-height: 1.8; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

@keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);} }
.reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); transition:opacity .7s,transform .7s; }
.reveal.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

@media(max-width:768px){
  nav { padding: 12px 16px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .hero-wrap, .wrap { padding: 0 20px; }
  .hero-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .servicios-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .porque-grid, .cot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; }
  .footer-info { text-align: left; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-logo-main">Conecta Seguros</div>
    <div class="nav-logo-sub">Te protegemos tu patrimonio</div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#servicios" class="nav-link">Coberturas</a>
    <a href="#porque" class="nav-link">Por qué elegirnos</a>
    <a href="#cotizar" class="nav-link">Cotizá</a>
  </div>
  <a href="#cotizar" class="nav-cta">Cotización online</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-wrap">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Asesoramiento profesional · Buenos Aires</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Protegé<br>
        lo que más<br>
        <em>importa.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Conectamos a cada cliente con <strong>las mejores aseguradoras del mercado</strong>, encontrando la cobertura exacta que necesita su patrimonio, su familia y su negocio.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="#cotizar" class="btn-primary">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/><path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.123.554 4.118 1.528 5.855L.057 23.886a.5.5 0 00.606.63l6.288-1.634A11.945 11.945 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 22c-1.886 0-3.655-.5-5.187-1.375l-.372-.215-3.854 1.002 1.036-3.742-.236-.386A9.96 9.96 0 012 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z"/></svg>
          Quiero mi cotización
        </a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="btn-secondary">Ver coberturas</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="hero-card-inner">
        <div class="hero-card-foto" style="background:none;padding:0;overflow:hidden;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 20%;" alt="Nicolás Álvarez"/></div>
        <div class="hero-card-nombre">Nicolás Álvarez</div>
        <div class="hero-card-cargo">Productor Asesor de Seguros</div>
        <div class="hero-card-mat">Matrícula SSN N.° 102.539</div>
        <div class="hero-card-aseg">
          <div class="aseg-item">Sancor Seguros</div>
          <div class="aseg-item">Mercantil Andina</div>
          <div class="aseg-item">Galicia Seguros</div>
          <div class="aseg-item">Rivadavia Seguros</div>
          <div class="aseg-item">Compañías de primer nivel</div>
          <div class="aseg-item">Asesoramiento confidencial</div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5493517315099?text=Hola%20Nicol%C3%A1s%2C%20quiero%20consultar%20sobre%20un%20seguro." target="_blank" class="hero-card-wa">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/><path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.123.554 4.118 1.528 5.855L.057 23.886a.5.5 0 00.606.63l6.288-1.634A11.945 11.945 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 22c-1.886 0-3.655-.5-5.187-1.375l-.372-.215-3.854 1.002 1.036-3.742-.236-.386A9.96 9.96 0 012 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10z"/></svg>
          Consultame ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICIOS -->
<section class="servicios reveal" id="servicios">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Coberturas disponibles</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Todo lo que<br><em>necesitás proteger.</em></h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">Trabajamos con las mejores aseguradoras del mercado para ofrecerte la cobertura exacta que tu situación requiere.</p>

    <div class="servicios-grid">
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">01</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🚗</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Automotor</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Responsabilidad civil, robo total y parcial, granizo, incendio. Cobertura especial para conductores de plataformas digitales como Uber, DiDi y Cabify.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">02</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🛰️</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Cobertura Satelital</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Localización y recupero del vehículo en caso de robo mediante tecnología GPS. Respuesta inmediata ante siniestros.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">03</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🏠</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Hogar</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Protección integral para tu vivienda. Incendio, robo, inundación, daños eléctricos y responsabilidad civil ante terceros.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">04</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🏥</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Accidente Personal</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Cobertura ante accidentes personales. Incapacidad temporaria o permanente, asistencia médica de urgencia y más.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">05</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🏍️</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Motos</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Responsabilidad civil obligatoria y coberturas ampliadas para motos de uso personal o reparto. Todos los modelos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="servicio-card">
        <div class="servicio-num">06</div>
        <div class="servicio-icon">🏪</div>
        <div class="servicio-titulo">Comercio</div>
        <p class="servicio-desc">Protección completa para tu negocio. Local, mercadería, robo, incendio, responsabilidad civil y ART.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- POR QUÉ -->
<section class="porque reveal" id="porque">
  <div class="wrap">
